88px;overflow:hidden\">          <h3>Event #55: &#8220;Writing effective website specification documents” by Mark Wilkinson</h3>          <p style=\"margin:5px 0;font-size:16px\">Tuesday, Mar 26, 2019,  6:00 PM</p>          <p style=\"margin: 0 0 5px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">The Old Sheriff Court (SYT)</span><br /><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">105 Brunswick St, Glasgow G1 1TF, GB</span></p>          <span style=\"color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;\">12 Members Attending</span>           <div style=\"margin:5px 0 10px\" class=\"mu_clearfix\">               <div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/e/2/a/thumb_249444106.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/b/0/2/thumb_40239682.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/1/2/4/thumb_279157156.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/8/5/thumb_283863717.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/5/f/1/thumb_272297905.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/4/4/8/thumb_252609288.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/c/5/2/thumb_247275442.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/9/b/a/thumb_245131162.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/c/c/thumb_283863276.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/9/a/a/thumb_257099818.jpeg\" /></div>          </div>          <p style=\"line-height:16px\">Do you want to set your website project up for success? Do you want to avoid any costly surprises along the way? Of course, you do. A thorough, focused web specification document will keep your web project runni